    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-01-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-01-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="154"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d154">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Chinese Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chinese Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-01-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 6, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 51.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of
                    your note of to-day’s date, in which you kindly inform me that you have received
                    absolutely certain information that the American proprietors of the Canton and
                    Hankau Railway, to meet the criticisms and objections <pb facs="0249" n="129"
                        xml:id="pg_129"/> which have been made in China to the concession, have
                    regained control of the complete ownership of a clear bona fide majority of the
                    entire stock of that company.</p>
                <p>In reply I have the honor to state that I have cabled your entire note to my
                    government for its consideration.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Chentung Liang-Cheng.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
